# simple cube

mtllib cube.mtl
o cube
v 0 0 0
v 0 0 1
v 0 1 1
v 0 1 0
v 1 0 0
v 1 0 1
v 1 1 1
v 1 1 0

vn -1  0  0
vn  1  0  0
vn  0 -1  0
vn  0  1  0
vn  0  0  1
vn  0  0 -1

usemtl Red
f 1//1 2//1 3//1 # left side
f 3//1 4//1 1//1
usemtl Yellow
f 5//2 7//2 6//2 # right side
f 7//2 5//2 8//2
usemtl Black
f 1//3 5//3 2//3 # bottom side
f 5//3 6//3 2//3
f 3//4 7//4 4//4 # upper side
f 7//4 8//4 4//4
usemtl Green
f 2//5 6//5 7//5 # front side
f 7//5 3//5 2//5
usemtl Blue
f 1//6 4//6 5//6 # back side
f 5//6 4//6 8//6